OL,5,G0000 Summer of '76: Away from It All
OL,6,     FHerbie and June Harris tell their
OL,7,     Fstory of the summer of 1976 and
OL,8,     Fhow they coped with their problems
OL,9,     Fand discovered the importance of
OL,10,     Fmaking the best of things - away
OL,11,     Ffrom it all.
OL,12,G0050 Keeping Up Appearances
OL,13,     F9/10. Comedy of social manners.
OL,14,     FHyacinth wants her neighbours to
OL,15,     Fsee the arrival of her new suite,
OL,16,     Fboasting that it's an exact
OL,17,     Freplica of one at Sandringham
OL,18,     FHouse.
